    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750350/extras/7021ed5465c0062200474b6951db9179.poster.avif?t=1702613231\" width=616 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750350/extras/7021ed5465c0062200474b6951db9179.webm?t=1702613231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750350/extras/7021ed5465c0062200474b6951db9179.mp4?t=1702613231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Sebil Engineering is a game about &quot;fixing&quot; roads. It features open ended gameplay, a branching level structure and levels designed to be solved in numerous different ways. Play in overhead view or drop down a surveyor tool to get right into the action in first person view, where you can explore the level on foot, adjust roads more precisely and try not to get yourself run over.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750350/extras/d66d2da7a787c8acda77404d005835a0.poster.avif?t=1702613231\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750350/extras/d66d2da7a787c8acda77404d005835a0.webm?t=1702613231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750350/extras/d66d2da7a787c8acda77404d005835a0.mp4?t=1702613231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 40+ Levels<br></li><li> Open ended gameplay with many solutions - play how you like<br></li><li> Branching level structure - choose where you go next<br></li><li> High detail traffic simulation<br></li><li> Realistic Civil Engineering</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750350/extras/c2549be7b162eb20404c54d96a9da8e3.poster.avif?t=1702613231\" width=616 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750350/extras/c2549be7b162eb20404c54d96a9da8e3.webm?t=1702613231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750350/extras/c2549be7b162eb20404c54d96a9da8e3.mp4?t=1702613231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
